name: Furniture_of_America_Nethera_Modern_Walnut_Console_Table
reviews: This is of great nice looking console table but price seems to be on a little higher side.Assembels in approx 2 hours, walnut color looks great.

Sturdy, solid, and just the right size. It holds a wider flatscreen tv, no problem. We needed a small footprint, narrow, but very stable table and this works perfectly. Have had it for a year and it is just like new.
Very nice cabinet for the price.
I have enjoyed the table. It sits in the entryway to my living room.
great product for the price, took a little while to assemble but beautiful once done
This is a very elegant piece of furniture for my hall way.
